Create bottom right chart in Non Graded 44

Step 1: Create bottom right chart in Non Graded

- Create a new column named Weekname with this Dax (Weekname = FORMAT(HW_Grading[DateEntered], "dddd"))

- Copy and Paste bottom left chart.

- Remove all of the shared axis and replace with Weekname and Hour of Day

- Select formatting under general, X position = 803, Y position = 435, Width = 477, Height = 284
